OL,5,FThe prospect of watching the Coronation
OL,6,Fled to a huge jump in the sales of
OL,7,Ftelevisions  helped too by the gradual
OL,8,Feasing of postwar austerity and
OL,9,Frestrictions.
OL,11,FAn episode of the much-loved ITV
OL,12,FSchools series How We Used to Live
OL,13,Fbroadcast in the early 80s  Your
OL,14,FUndoubted Queen  interweaved the story
OL,15,Fof Coronation Day with the Hodgkins'
OL,16,Ffamily getting their first television.
OL,17,F(This edition of the programme can be
OL,18,Ffound on YouTube.)
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G3/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
