PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1667072492
OL,5,FIt is interesting to contemplate
OL,6,Fwhether television in Britain would
OL,7,Fhave taken off quite so rapidly without
OL,8,Fthe boost of the Coronation.
OL,10,FIt is easy to imagine a more gradual
OL,11,Fincrease in penetration. Had this
OL,12,Fhappened, would television have become
OL,13,Fquite such a part of Britain's popular
OL,14,Fculture so early?
OL,16,FWithout the rapid increase in sales
OL,17,Fwould the new ITV companies  which did
OL,18,Fstruggle to begin with in 1955 and 1956
OL,19,F have become quite so lucrative so
OL,20,Fquickly?
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G4/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35505
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1667072492
OL,5,FOf course, there's no doubt television
OL,6,Fwould have gradually taken off in
OL,7,FBritain as it did in every other
OL,8,Fcomparable country.
OL,10,FWith the BBC at the centre of the
OL,11,Fsystem it would always be a worthwhile
OL,12,Fendeavour  attempting to make a wide
OL,13,Frange of programmes including some of
OL,14,Fgenuine distinction and importance.
OL,16,FBut without the booster rocket of the
OL,17,FCoronation the path may have been
OL,18,Fdifferent.
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G5/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35506
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1667072492
OL,5,FCoronation Day itself provided the
OL,6,Fnovelty of almost uninterrupted viewing
OL,7,Ffrom mid-morning until late evening.
OL,9,FInterestingly Radio Times even billed
OL,10,Fthe tuning signal  broadcast much
OL,11,Fearlier than usual  which presumably
OL,12,Fwas to help with last minute TV
OL,13,Finstallations.
OL,15,FLater on it is interesting to note how
OL,16,Fmany other Royal occasions over the
OL,17,Fyears were pivotal to the story of
OL,18,Ftelevision's development.
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G6/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
