OL,5,FThe Investiture of the Prince of Wales
OL,6,Fin 1969  shown while only BBC Two was
OL,7,Fin colour  was one of the events which
OL,8,Fhighlighted that colour television here
OL,9,Fwas true and natural.
OL,11,FThe Mexico Olympics the previous year
OL,12,Fundoubtedly attracted interest to
OL,13,Fcolour television but the converted
OL,14,FNTSC picture quality may not have been
OL,15,Fquite so impressive as the high quality
OL,16,FPAL images.
OL,18,FFour years later, the wedding of
OL,19,FPrincess Anne gave a big boost to the
OL,20,Fsale of colour sets which were, by
OL,21,Fthen, becoming much more affordable.
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G7/10
