OL,5,FIt is also worth noting just how
OL,6,Fcentral the BBC has been to so many
OL,7,FRoyal events over the years, even when
OL,8,FITV provided equally good  or arguably
OL,9,Fbetter  coverage.
OL,11,FIt highlights the importance of the BBC
OL,12,Fas one of the pillars of national life
OL,13,Fat the moments when we come together.
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
OL,22,                                  G8/10
