OL,5,FThere's been a reminder of that in
OL,6,Frecent days. In the immediate aftermath
OL,7,Fof The Queen's death the BBC's audience
OL,8,Fwas much higher than normal. Others
OL,9,Fwere similar to normal or even slightly
OL,10,Fsmaller  this is no reflection of the
OL,11,Fwork of individuals. Some tiny digital
OL,12,Fchannels were completely irrelevant.
OL,14,FMany writers and commentators have
OL,15,Fobserved that the passing of the Queen
OL,16,Ftruly marks the end of an era in
OL,17,FBritish history.
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television
